40，一個都唔止40"},{"pid":"090a0cd4f039d71f169d332f9647ef8e86702098","tid":894390,"uid":142855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe689504c9d2084089e3571ee903dadb729a11f3","tid":894390,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/145435_08be2aa0dd2179c6a2f5111a18d912fc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F145435_08be2aa0dd2179c6a2f5111a18d912fc.gif&h=b0391598&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T16:11:20.000Z","msg":"笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4497050d723e079f1835ed61e97aa6a84fa103","tid":894390,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5959ec420992d5ddee0d4b9739991373718f97d5","tid":894390,"uid":155225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"會計師無可能加埋40，一個都唔止40"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"九成local firm d 19 auditor"},{"pid":"14b0295be3da3dd65eae4b56fbc40b062a7cd975","tid":894390,"uid":31305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T16:19:44.000Z","msg":"80後 做左野都起碼六七年唔掛<br />\n仲要自稱會計師，有咩可能一個人得兩萬幾咁少"},{"pid":"ff7289bf22d44f592781868579a6f8b3b8c73ab2","tid":894390,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9aa23f9fbb0b1476522a3cd5dcf06c12697b56","tid":894390,"uid":11973,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e55f2e5be09b4063a2eb265acb80dbced2dd4feb","tid":894390,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:15:20.000Z","msg":"過去努力追求學位、事業，最後卻換不來人生最基本需要與尊嚴的住所，<br />\n過去努力追求學位、事業，最後卻換不來人生最基本需要與尊嚴的住所，<br />\n過去努力追求學位、事業，最後卻換不來人生最基本需要與尊嚴的住所，<br />\n過去努力追求學位、事業，最後卻換不來人生最基本需要與尊嚴的住所，"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T17:51:58.000Z","msg":"諗起以前高登教父講嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死讀爛讀...死讀爛讀...<br />\n死讀爛讀完最後先發覺原來今日香港樓契值錢過沙紙咁多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真你80後機會已經多過班90後好多啦<br />\n食唔到08/09年嗰個跌浪都食到15年啦吓話<br />\n嗰時買到樓而家發撚咗喇<br />\n就算冇買樓都識買QQ呀嘛??<br />\n打你09年買今年年頭放隨時仲賺得多過你買樓啦<br />\n夠俾首期有凸㖭喇<br />\n仲話會計師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n卅幾歲人無理由連投資理財都唔識自己戶口條數都管唔掂呀嘛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家先醒覺自己買唔起會唔會遲咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n堂堂專業人士淪落到要抽居屋?<br />\n專業人士仲要80後即係起碼做咗十年八年嘢<br />\n唔會兩個戶口加埋連1-2M都冇呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面大把同年紀就算做地盤三行都買到私樓啦已經<br />\n做到師傅級判頭嗰班而家幾層樓收租㖭喇<br />\n不過我都欣賞佢話置咗業先生仔呢個諗法嘅<br />\n算係負責任嘅表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係租多兩年樓老婆都就變高齡產婦<br />\n不如繼續努力ot做租租過世好過啦<br />\n自己冇仔女咪當交租係助養業主啲仔女囉<br />\n都算係積福嘅一種嚟嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782b8fb3c6f8d810d201c645579797fe726f06db","tid":894390,"uid":7790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T17:55:43.000Z","msg":"黃子華都講過，係香港你一係做富豪，一係訓天橋底。<br />\n無公屋住既話全香港天橋底加埋都未必夠位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b9d56e9cc8d9c3066c72c0d91053e9e5198c5f","tid":894390,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T17:59:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b8b8da2beba95a56f79875be81349c245c220f1","tid":894390,"uid":91443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"佢依家租緊樓係咪叫租奴？"},{"pid":"c0b903cecb1a8ccbee2ad9f925c72852dbfce93d","tid":894390,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:59:08.000Z","msg":"兩人作為專業人士，月入逾4萬多元<br />\n會員文員 定 會計司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"}]}